</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Lives</td><td>33420,0:33452,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lives = x</td><td>33199,x (x= 1-255)</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR><B>Change x to whatever value you wish, using the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI</B>
<BR><BR><B>If anyone finds out if this works, <a href="mailto:tipshop@ysrnry.co.uk">let me know</A></B>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
